Acme-CPANAuthors-InMemoriam
===========================

This module was created to remember those CPAN Authors who are no longer with
us, who have given us their inspiration in the form of code, to continue and
celebrate their time with us.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these modules:

  Acme::CPANAuthors

For testing the module requires these modules:

  IO::File
  Test::More

For optional testing the module would like these modules:

  Test::CPAN::Meta
  Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON
  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

